name: QUEEN SERAPHINE
description: Seraphine grew and developed in the wizarding academy which made her very proficient in using magic. She also became the best student in the academy. After graduating from the academy he carried out the duties of a magician, namely traveling and helping everyone in need. Until she met a good king and they finally got married. One day a war broke out between the kingdoms and resulted in the destruction of the whole country. Seraphine who was fed up after seeing the devastation across the country finally fled the refugee area. Towards the vanguard with his red rose teleportation magic she slaughtered all opponents. The incident immediately aroused the enthusiasm of the soldiers and made the moment a counterattack. Seraphine used all her abilities to attack and protect the ranks. Finally all the enemy soldiers had been defeated and she went to the enemy defense to kill the enemy leader and bring his head before the king.
